OOC: Hey Dewboy, i think you have the wrong idea about us council members.  
Our purpose is not, "look for things to call illegal".  We are just the 
governors of this RPG, and we try to make things fair for everyone.  We have 
to be careful, or the RPG will be ruined with an arms race, like the one 
before i joined.

--part1_93.d6a2806.288830b3_boundary
